<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Support - SecureBank</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar', { user: user }) %>
    
    <div class="dashboard-container">
        <h2>💬 Customer Support</h2>
        
        <div class="support-options">
            <div class="support-card">
                <div class="support-icon">📞</div>
                <h3>Call Us</h3>
                <p>+91-1800-XXX-XXXX</p>
                <p class="support-time">24/7 Available</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="support-card">
                <div class="support-icon">✉️</div>
                <h3>Email Support</h3>
                <p>support@securebank.com</p>
                <p class="support-time">Reply within 24 hours</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="support-card">
                <div class="support-icon">💬</div>
                <h3>Live Chat</h3>
                <button class="btn-primary">Start Chat</button>
                <p class="support-time">Online now</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-section">
            <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>How do I reset my password?</h4>
                <p>Go to Settings > Security > Change Password</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>How long does a transfer take?</h4>
                <p>Transfers are instant within SecureBank. External transfers may take 1-2 business days.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>What are the interest rates?</h4>
                <p>Fixed Deposits: 7.5% p.a. | Recurring Deposits: 7% p.a. | Loans: 8.5% p.a.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>How do I download my statement?</h4>
                <p>Go to Transactions > Download Statement > Select date range and format (PDF/Text)</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>Is my money safe?</h4>
                <p>Yes! All deposits are insured and we use bank-level encryption for all transactions.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-form-section">
            <h3>Raise a Support Ticket</h3>
            <form class="support-form">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Subject</label>
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Brief description of your issue" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Category</label>
                    <select required>
                        <option value="">Select Category</option>
                        <option value="account">Account Issues</option>
                        <option value="transaction">Transaction Problem</option>
                        <option value="card">Card Related</option>
                        <option value="loan">Loan Enquiry</option>
                        <option value="other">Other</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Message</label>
                    <textarea rows="5" placeholder="Describe your issue in detail..." required></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Submit Ticket</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
